 the general perjury statute under Federal law defines perjury as a felony and provides for a prison sentence of up to five years."<BR><BR>from <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Perjury" target="_blank">http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Perjury</a>

              

              
              
